        <Relationship_Type>Parent/Child</Relationship_Type>
        <Historic_Flag>Current</Historic_Flag>
        <Parent_String>papermaking tools and equipment [300023388], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices used for macerating fibers, usually from rags, into a pulp to be used for papermaking. Specifically: a hand-operated device with a handle and hammer-head fixed to a support, that is raised and lowered successively to pound the material beneath.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000020511/Hunter, Papermaking: History of an Ancient Craft (1947)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Vorrichtung zum Auswaschen von Fasern, in der Regel aus Lumpen, um eine Pulpe für die Papierherstellung zu gewinnen. Insbesondere ein Handwerkzeug mit Griff und hammerähnlichem Kopf, das auf eine Stütze befestigt ist und fortwährend gehoben und gesenkt wird, um darunter gelegenes Material zu stampfen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Apparaten die gebruikt worden om vezels, meestal van lappen, tot pulp te stampen voor het papiermaken. Specifiek een handbediend apparaat met een handvat en een hamerkop, bevestigd aan een steun, dat achtereenvolgens omhoog en omlaag wordt gebracht om op het materiaal eronder te stampen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
